PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the WHITECAP DAKOTA/SIOUX FIRST NATION BAND surrenders, for a term of 100 years, some 463.7 hectares of land on White Cap Indian Reserve No. 94 in Saskatchewan, for the purpose of leasing them to a corporation wholly-owned by the Band for residential, commercial or recreational purposes.
